org.apache.archiva.components.registry

Interface Registry

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommonsConfigurationRegistry

    public interface Registry
    The Plexus registry is a single source of external configuration for Plexus components and applications. It can be used by components to source configuration, knowing that it can be used from within applications without the information being hard coded into the component.

      • addChangeListener

        void addChangeListener(RegistryListener listener)
        Add a change listener. Note that settings this on the base registry will only detect 'invalidation' events, not individual changes. You should retrieve the named sub-registry to listen for changes. TODO: this isn't ideal, so maybe fix combined configuration to re-fire it's events to it's own listeners in the c-c implementation
        Parameters:
        listener - the listener
